elm-refactor dev

Usage: elm-format [--upgrade UPGRADE_DEFINITION] INPUT
  Refactor Elm source files.

Available options:
  -h,--help                Show this help text
  --upgrade UPGRADE_DEFINITION
                           A file specifying an upgrade transformation to apply.
                           You may specify this more than once.
  INPUT                    The .elm file to transform. You may specify more than
                           one.

Examples:
  elm-refactor Upgrade.elm Main.elm      # refactors Main.elm
  elm-refactor Upgrade.elm src/          # refactors all *.elm files in the src directory
